snippet.title: Rogue Legends | Coming Soon to Bloons TD 6!
snippet.description:
Legends are DLC expansions of the classic Bloons TD 6 play. Each Legends expansion will bring new visuals, challenges, and entirely new gameplay that pushes BTD 6 in fun and dynamic new directions. Here's all you need to know about the first of these expansions; Rogue Legends!

Let us know your thoughts in the comments below :D
